sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as External Client
    participant AuthProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Sidecar (RHOAI 3.x)
    participant REST as REST Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as gRPC Server<br/>8081/TCP gRPC
    participant DP as DataPlane Handler
    participant Cache as Response Cache
    participant Batcher as Adaptive Batcher
    participant Registry as MultiModelRegistry
    participant Model as MLModel Runtime<br/>(sklearn/xgboost/lgbm/onnx)
    participant Storage as /mnt/models<br/>Model Artifacts
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>8082/TCP
    participant OTel as OpenTelemetry<br/>Collector

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,Model: Flow 1: REST Inference Request
        Client->>AuthProxy: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Bearer Token
        AuthProxy->>REST: Forward (authenticated)
        REST->>DP: InferenceRequest
        DP->>Cache: Check cache
        Cache-->>DP: Cache miss
        DP->>Batcher: Queue request
        Batcher->>Registry: Batched InferenceRequest
        Registry->>Model: predict(request)
        Model-->>Registry: InferenceResponse
        Registry-->>Batcher: Response
        Batcher-->>DP: Split responses
        DP->>Cache: Store response
        DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
        REST-->>AuthProxy: JSON Response
        AuthProxy-->>Client: 200 OK + JSON
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client,Model: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
        Client->>AuthProxy: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC
        AuthProxy->>GRPC: Forward
        GRPC->>GRPC: Protobuf → InferenceRequest
        GRPC->>DP: infer()
        DP->>Registry: route to model
        Registry->>Model: predict(request)
        Model-->>Registry: InferenceResponse
        Registry-->>DP: Response
        DP-->>GRPC: InferenceResponse
        GRPC->>GRPC: InferenceResponse → Protobuf
        GRPC-->>AuthProxy: ModelInferResponse
        AuthProxy-->>Client: gRPC Response
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Storage,Model: Flow 3: Model Loading at Startup
        Note over Storage: Storage Initializer<br/>populates /mnt/models
        Model->>Model: Validate trusted-runtimes.json
        Model->>Storage: Scan model-settings.json files
        Storage-->>Model: Model configurations
        Model->>Model: Dynamic import of runtime class
        Model->>Storage: Load model artifacts<br/>(.joblib, .onnx, .bst, etc.)
        Storage-->>Model: Model data
        Model->>Registry: Register model (ready)
    end

    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Note over Prom,OTel: Flow 4: Observability
        Prom->>REST: GET /metrics (port 8082)
        REST-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics
        REST->>OTel: Traces (OTLP/gRPC)
        GRPC->>OTel: Traces (OTLP/gRPC)
    end
